stateDiagram-v2
    direction LR
    [*] --> created: Agent /agent/create
    created --> on_going: Dispatcher /dispatch
    on_going --> assigned: unit event
    assigned --> accepted: unit accepts
    accepted --> en_route: unit departs
    en_route --> arrived: unit on scene
    arrived --> on_action: unit engaged
    on_action --> completed: unit finishes
    completed --> [*]

    note right of created
        event_source = agent
        only valid first event
    end note

    note right of on_going
        event_source = dispatcher
        writes unit_id[] + unit_details[]
    end note

    note left of completed
        terminal — further unit
        events rejected with 409
    end note
